snippet.title: Jack 3 The Future Trailer
snippet.description:
Erm, THAT just happened.

This is the trailer for my upcoming Jacksfilms RPG fangame called "Jack 3 the Future". It's built off of RPG Maker 2003. It's basically a spiritual successor to Jack to the Future, one of @jacksfilms's most infamous videos. I do not claim to be a video editor, I am not a very good video editor at all, and this is edited very poorly, but uhhhh yeah, just kinda wanted to throw something together.

Play the demo here! It's around 40% of what the full game's length will be.
https://rbxgemini.itch.io/jack3thefuture

Music is a remixed version of Jacksfilms's "Twitter for Android" that's used in J3TF.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ujZcM-DSamA
